Class MovableEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • uc3m.bomberman.entity.Entity
      • uc3m.bomberman.entity.MovableEntity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Player

    public abstract class MovableEntity
extends Entity
    This class extends the Entity and holds the methods neccesary for every movable entity such as the enemies and the player.
